item.title: Who am I?
item.description: I am an Embedded Software Engineer by trade, a Mechanical Engineer by degree, and a less than average tinkerer by hobby. I have plenty of hobbies and figured I would use this site as a catchall where I can document everything I do. I’m not quite sure what this will become but for now it is a fun project to keep track of what I do as the new year begins.
